Silver morion quest
White only
Enter Ithildir's room 2n u from greenery in the new west Lorien zone and he will start talking. When he asks you 'Are you seeking safety, adventure, or fighting our common foe?', say 'adventure'. He will continue talking and nod after he has asked to help him. Then he asks you to bring home  Annariel Tingliwinde and gives you a beryl ring, so that she recognizes you as the messenger for him.

Annariel is taken prisoner in OOC, north from orc prisoner and is guarded by Adrahar, who flees when you enter.

Give the beryl ring to Annariel and group when she starts following you.
Take her out from the OOC and protect her. On Redhorn pass you will be ambushed by orc patrol and Adrahar. A Morgundul uruk plants a solid kick in Annariel Tingliwinde's rib-cage, who collapses and falls to the ground. Kill them and cure or heal Annariel and continue moving to Ithildir. On bad, Adrahar can flee and you might miss the kill.

When you arrive to Ithildir, he rewards you with a silver morion
Reward: silver morion
Achievment: You have rescued Annariel Tingliwinde from captivity.
Level: 4 legends
